  <brief_title>Safety and Tolerance Study of Alpha-Lactalbumin Enriched and Probiotic-Supplemented Infant Formula in Infants With Colic</brief_title>
  <official_title>Study of Growth and Gastrointestinal Tolerance of an Alpha-Lactalbumin Enriched and Probiotic-Supplemented Infant Formula in Infants With Colic.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
